      "content": "it's not just a \"dark chapter\" though. it feels more like the end. like i've run out of road. everyone expects me to just pick myself up and try a new angle or find a new grant, but there's nothing left in me to try. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to be able to sleep and not feel this constant, heavy dread in my chest. i just want peace.",
